Both Namibia and Netherlands will be keen to continue their winning run and consolidate their position in the Qualifiers points table.

Namibia won their last meeting against the Netherlands in the 2021 T20 World Cup by six wickets with one over to spare.

The Dutch side holds the edge in overall T20I records after winning two games against Namibia.
